events.title: Vibecoding
events.desc: We'll be looking at vibecoding best practices and different programs created with vibe coders in mind. We'll spend most of the meeting attempting a vibecoding workshop / competition. Results should be available on this website by Friday, Oct 17.

events.title: Reading Group: Learning Transferable Visual Models From Natural Language Supervision
